# Media-pipeline hygiene: track the SCAFFOLD, config, scripts and docs — NEVER the heavy media.
# Source clips, audio, captions, work renders, masters and exports are engine outputs, not source code.
*.mov
*.mp4
*.mkv
*.wav
*.aif
*.aiff
*.mp3
*.prores
*.exr
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg

# ...but DO keep the structure + config + tooling.
!.gitkeep
!asset_manifest.json
!AUTOMATION_MATRIX.md
!pipeline/**
!README.md
